high_descs: Turn left, go to the bed.
Pick up the book next to the stuffed animal on the bed.
Turn around, go to the right side of the desk.
Put the book to the left of the vase on the desk.
Turn around, go to the safe, turn right to the bed.
Pick up the book on the bed.
Turn right, go to the right side of the desk.
Put the book to the right of the vase on the desk.
anns.task_desc: Put the books on the desk.

high_descs: Turn around, face the bed to your right and go to the bed.
Pick up a book with the name Deep Learning directly next to the panda bear toy.
Turn around and go to the wooden desk.
Put the book down on the desk to the left of two white containers.
Turn right, go to the door, turn right, and cross the room to the white safe, and turn right to face the end of the bed.
Pick up a book with the name Deep Learning near the left end of the bed.
Turn right and go to the edge of the bed, turn left and go towards the small wooden dresser, turn right and go to the large wooden desk.
Place the book onto the wooden desk to the right of the two white containers.
anns.task_desc: Place two books on the wooden desk.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the right to go to the bed.
Pick up a book near the stuffed animal on the bed.
Turn around and go to the yellow desk on the other side of the wall.
Put the book on the desk near the first bowl.
Walk to the right, turn right  near the door, walk straight to the white cabinet and face the bed.
Grab another book from on top of the bed.
Walk to the right, turn left and turn right to go back to the yellow desk.
Put The book to the right of the first book on the desk.
anns.task_desc: Put 2 books side by side near the bowl on the yellow desk.

high_descs: Turn left, proceed to bed.
Pick up book directly left of panda bear.
Turn around, proceed to desk.
Place book sideways on desk, to the left of the basket and to the right of the left phone.
Turn right, proceed to door.  Turn right and proceed to safe.  Turn right to face foot of bed.
Pick up book off of bed.
Go around bed then turn right and proceed to desk.
Place book on desk, sideways, to the right of the other book and basket.
Turn left and face the bed.
Pick up the book closest to the laptop.
Turn around and walk straight ahead to the desk.
Place the book on the desk in front of and to the left of the glasses.
Turn around and walk back to the bed.
Pick up the book on the bed.
Turn around and walk back to the desk.
Place the book to the right of the other book.
anns.task_desc: Put two books on a desk.

high_descs: Turn left and move to stand facing the center of the bed.
Pick up the book closest to the stuffed bear.
Turn around and carry the book to the desk.
Place the book on the desk to the right of the chair.
Cross the room to stand at the foot of the bed.
Pick up the remaining book from the bed.
Turn right and carry the book to the desk.
Place the book on the desk to the right of the book you previously placed there.
anns.task_desc: Move two books to the desk.
